Package: sprintr
Title: Light weight interface to the Atlassian Jira API
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Severski", email = "davidski@deadheaven.com", role = c("cre", "aut"), comment = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-7867-0459"),
    person("Susana", "Quartin", email = "susanaquartin@gmail.com", role = c("ctb")))
Description: `sprintr` provides a minimal interface to the Jira and Jira 
    Software APIs. Targetting scrum and kanban boards, sprintr allows pulling 
    read-only information from Jira, enabling metrics to be retrieved and 
    processed in R. This includes analyzing issues, sprint velocity, and 
    other common agile metrics.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
